A confident businessperson standing before a large whiteboard covered in colorful hand-drawn diagrams, flowcharts, and visual sketches, their arm mid-motion as they draw with a bright marker. The whiteboard displays abstract interconnected shapes, arrows, and simple icons representing ideas flowing together. The scene is rendered in a warm, tasteful illustrative style with soft watercolor textures and muted earth tones. The perspective is from the audience's viewpoint, showing the presenter's dynamic energy and the organic, creative nature of the visual storytelling. Scattered markers in various colors rest on the whiteboard ledge. Warm afternoon light streams through a nearby window, casting gentle shadows across the scene.
